&lt;h1 class=&quot;PDq2pG_selectionAnchorContainer&quot; data-start=&quot;674&quot; data-end=&quot;720&quot;&gt;Customer Service Representative / Dispatcher&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;721&quot; data-end=&quot;766&quot;&gt;Gaithersburg Garage Doors | Rockville, MD&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;768&quot; data-end=&quot;826&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;768&quot; data-end=&quot;826&quot;&gt;Home Service Experience Preferred | Hiring Immediately&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;828&quot; data-end=&quot;1004&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;828&quot; data-end=&quot;1004&quot;&gt;Have you worked in HVAC, plumbing, electrical, garage doors, roofing, restoration, appliance repair, pest control, landscaping, or another fast-paced home service business?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1006&quot; data-end=&quot;1194&quot;&gt;If you&#39;re experienced at managing busy phone lines, coordinating technicians, scheduling appointments, and keeping customers informed throughout the service process, we&#39;d love to meet you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1196&quot; data-end=&quot;1428&quot;&gt;Gaithersburg Garage Doors is growing, and we&#39;re looking for an experienced Customer Service Representative/Dispatcher who thrives in a fast-paced service environment and enjoys helping customers while keeping technicians productive.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1430&quot; data-end=&quot;1573&quot;&gt;This is an opportunity to build a long-term career with an established company that values teamwork, customer service, and professional growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1575&quot; data-end=&quot;1578&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;1580&quot; data-end=&quot;1597&quot;&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1599&quot; data-end=&quot;1684&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll serve as the communication hub between our customers and field technicians by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1686&quot; data-end=&quot;2342&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1686&quot; data-end=&quot;1737&quot;&gt;Answering a high volume of inbound customer calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1738&quot; data-end=&quot;1806&quot;&gt;Scheduling service appointments and coordinating technician routes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1807&quot; data-end=&quot;1872&quot;&gt;Dispatching technicians while balancing priority and efficiency&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1873&quot; data-end=&quot;1926&quot;&gt;Communicating appointment updates and arrival times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1927&quot; data-end=&quot;2003&quot;&gt;Following up with customers regarding completed work and service questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2004&quot; data-end=&quot;2056&quot;&gt;Assisting customers through phone, email, and text&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2057&quot; data-end=&quot;2109&quot;&gt;Creating and maintaining accurate customer records&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2110&quot; data-end=&quot;2176&quot;&gt;Supporting technicians with job information and schedule changes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2177&quot; data-end=&quot;2245&quot;&gt;Identifying opportunities for additional services when appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2246&quot; data-end=&quot;2342&quot;&gt;Delivering an exceptional customer experience from the first phone call through job completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr data-start=&quot;2344&quot; data-end=&quot;2347&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2 data-start=&quot;2349&quot; data-end=&quot;2382&quot;&gt;We&#39;re Looking For Someone With&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2384&quot; data-end=&quot;2500&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;2384&quot; data-end=&quot;2500&quot;&gt;2+ years of customer service, dispatch, or scheduling experience in a home service or field service environment.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2502&quot; data-end=&quot;2535&quot;&gt;Experience in industr

&lt;p data-start=&quot;149&quot; data-end=&quot;233&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;149&quot; data-end=&quot;233&quot;&gt;Now Hiring: Experienced Dispatcher – Join Our Fast-Paced, Customer-Focused Team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;235&quot; data-end=&quot;636&quot;&gt;Are you a skilled communicator and natural multitasker with a knack for staying organized under pressure? We’re seeking a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;357&quot; data-end=&quot;392&quot;&gt;dynamic, experienced Dispatcher&lt;/strong&gt; to coordinate and manage daily schedules for technicians, customers, and trade managers across multiple departments. If you thrive in a fast-paced environment and love being at the center of a high-energy team, this is the opportunity for you!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;667&quot;&gt;📍&lt;strong data-start=&quot;640&quot; data-end=&quot;653&quot;&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Rockville Office&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr data-start=&quot;669&quot; data-end=&quot;672&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;674&quot; data-end=&quot;697&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;678&quot; data-end=&quot;697&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;699&quot; data-end=&quot;1656&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;699&quot; data-end=&quot;818&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;701&quot; data-end=&quot;818&quot;&gt;Efficiently assign and route maintenance and repair calls based on technician location, availability, and skillset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;819&quot; data-end=&quot;948&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;821&quot; data-end=&quot;948&quot;&gt;Manage and update schedules in real-time while maintaining ongoing communication with technicians, customers, and management.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;949&quot; data-end=&quot;1056&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;951&quot; data-end=&quot;1056&quot;&gt;Review daily calls to ensure accuracy in skill level, parts, special instructions, and payment methods.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1057&quot; data-end=&quot;1145&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1059&quot; data-end=&quot;1145&quot;&gt;Optimize technician routes to reduce travel time, cut costs, and prevent call backs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1146&quot; data-end=&quot;1291&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1148&quot; data-end=&quot;1291&quot;&gt;Serve as a key point of contact—explaining services, answering scheduling questions, and helping customers understand home warranty policies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1292&quot; data-end=&quot;1388&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1294&quot; data-end=&quot;1388&quot;&gt;Document customer interactions and ensure timely follow-ups by the appropriate team members.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1389&quot; data-end=&quot;1492&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1391&quot; data-end=&quot;1492&quot;&gt;Handle incoming calls and direct them to the correct personnel with professionalism and efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1493&quot; data-end=&quot;1592&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1495&quot; data-end=&quot;1592&quot;&gt;Be prepared to work extended hours as needed and maintain high levels of customer satisfaction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1593&quot; data-end=&quot;1656&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1595&quot; data-end=&quot;1656&quot;&gt;Take on additional tasks as assigned to support team success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1658&quot; data-end=&quot;1661&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1663&quot; data-end=&quot;1699&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;1667&quot; data-end=&quot;1699&quot;&gt;What You Bring to the Table:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1701&quot; data-end=&quot;2336&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1701&quot; data-end=&quot;1748&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1703&quot; data-end=&quot;1748&quot;&gt;High School Diploma

&lt;h1 data-start=&quot;314&quot; data-end=&quot;359&quot;&gt;🚪 Garage Door Technician – Rockville, MD&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;360&quot; data-end=&quot;422&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;360&quot; data-end=&quot;420&quot;&gt;Gaithersburg Garage Doors | Family-Owned | Career Growth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;360&quot; data-end=&quot;422&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;360&quot; data-end=&quot;420&quot;&gt;Pay: Total compensation after training $80K-100K. $20-30/hr during training&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;424&quot; data-end=&quot;636&quot;&gt;Do you love working with people, solving problems, and making a real impact in your community? At &lt;strong data-start=&quot;522&quot; data-end=&quot;551&quot;&gt;Gaithersburg Garage Doors&lt;/strong&gt;, we’re not just opening garage doors—we’re opening the door to a rewarding career.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;831&quot;&gt;We’re looking for a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;658&quot; data-end=&quot;705&quot;&gt;positive, personable Garage Door Technician&lt;/strong&gt; who thrives in a fast-paced environment, enjoys hands-on work, and is eager to grow with a respected, family-owned company.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;833&quot; data-end=&quot;851&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;852&quot; data-end=&quot;1361&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;852&quot; data-end=&quot;930&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;854&quot; data-end=&quot;930&quot;&gt;Install, service, and repair garage doors, openers, and related equipment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;931&quot; data-end=&quot;1023&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;933&quot; data-end=&quot;1023&quot;&gt;Conduct detailed inspections and ensure all work meets top safety and quality standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1024&quot; data-end=&quot;1097&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1026&quot; data-end=&quot;1097&quot;&gt;Keep accurate records of work, including notes, diagrams, and photos.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1098&quot; data-end=&quot;1221&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1100&quot; data-end=&quot;1221&quot;&gt;Maintain a professional, customer-first attitude—always looking for solutions and opportunities to go above and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1222&quot; data-end=&quot;1292&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1224&quot; data-end=&quot;1292&quot;&gt;Collaborate with teammates and cross-train to strengthen the team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1293&quot; data-end=&quot;1361&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1295&quot; data-end=&quot;1361&quot;&gt;Stay safety-focused, following OSHA best practices at all times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1363&quot; data-end=&quot;1389&quot;&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1390&quot; data-end=&quot;1862&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1390&quot; data-end=&quot;1440&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1392&quot; data-end=&quot;1440&quot;&gt;Valid driver’s license &amp;amp; clean driving record.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1441&quot; data-end=&quot;1565&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1443&quot; data-end=&quot;1565&quot;&gt;Mechanical aptitude—experience with sectional, rolling steel, fire doors, high-speed doors, or dock equipment is a plus.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1566&quot; data-end=&quot;1638&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1568&quot; data-end=&quot;1638&quot;&gt;Comfortable lifting 75+ lbs, climbing ladders, and using hand tools.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1639&quot; data-end=&quot;1692&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1641&quot; data-end=&quot;1692&quot;&gt;Strong customer service and communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1693&quot; data-end=&quot;1768&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1695&quot; data-end=&quot;1768&quot;&gt;Ability to problem-s

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;422&quot; data-end=&quot;435&quot;&gt;About Us:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;437&quot; data-end=&quot;765&quot;&gt;At Gaithersburg Garage Doors, we specialize in high-quality garage door installation, service, and repair. With a commitment to craftsmanship and customer satisfaction, we’ve built a reputation as a trusted name in our community. Whether it’s residential or commercial, we’re proud to provide fast, reliable, and friendly service.&lt;/p&gt;
