&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1157&quot; data-end=&quot;1178&quot;&gt;What We Look For:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1180&quot; data-end=&quot;1479&quot;&gt;✅ Strong work ethic and punctuality&lt;br data-start=&quot;1215&quot; data-end=&quot;1218&quot;&gt;✅ Willingness to learn and take direction&lt;br data-start=&quot;1259&quot; data-end=&quot;1262&quot;&gt;✅ Basic mechanical or construction skills (a plus but not required)&lt;br data-start=&quot;1329&quot; data-end=&quot;1332&quot;&gt;✅ Clean driving record (for field positions)&lt;br data-start=&quot;1376&quot; data-end=&quot;1379&quot;&gt;✅ Great customer service attitude&lt;br data-start=&quot;1412&quot; data-end=&quot;1415&quot;&gt;✅ Ability to lift 50+ lbs and work in various weather conditions&lt;/p&gt;
